{"tid":2132043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美心上半年蝕近 4 億　牛奶國際：盈利大減源於美心表現差","createTime":"2020-07-30T08:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T09:45:48.000Z","uid":36494,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"520f3e45b2972cdd0ed2d677baf7f00be3ad80df","tid":2132043,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"牛奶國際（SGX: DFIH）公布 2020 年上半年業績，股東盈利只有 1.15 億美元，按年大跌 35%。當中牛奶國際持有 5 成權益的美心營業額按年同期大跌近 3 成，只有 8.73 億美元。由於美心拖累牛奶國際虧損 2,500 萬美元，而牛奶國際持有美心 5 成權益，換言之<span class=\"red\">美心上半年虧損 5,000 萬美元（3.9 億港元）。</span><br />\n<br />\n牛奶國際指，武漢肺炎疫情令到旗下的美心、健美品牌，以及便利店業務的利潤貢獻大減，公司的盈利亦大跌，但是雜貨零售和家居業務表現強勁。牛奶國際並且表示，<span class=\"red\">聯營及合資公司貢獻的基本利潤錄得明顯下跌的主要原因，是由於美心表現欠佳，令集團基本盈利減少 4 成，至只有 1.05 億美元。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E8%9D%95%E8%BF%91-4-%E5%84%84-%E7%89%9B%E5%A5%B6%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%9B%E6%BA%90%E6%96%BC%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%B7%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BF%2583%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25BF%2591-4-%25E5%2584%2584-%25E7%2589%259B%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E7%259B%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B8%259B%25E6%25BA%2590%25E6%2596%25BC%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25B7%25AE%2F&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDShAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=309bed07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BF%2583%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25BF%2591-4-%25E5%2584%2584-%25E7%2589%259B%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E7%259B%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B8%259B%25E6%25BA%2590%25E6%2596%25BC%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25B7%25AE%2F&h=ca690fc6\" data